      <title>英国抵押贷款债券风险高，因拖欠还款面临现金流压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/risky-uk-mortgage-bonds-face-cash-flow-pressure-as-arrears-soar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级表示，对于债务被捆绑成住宅抵押贷款支持证券的英国较弱房主而言，他们在贷款到期时偿还本金的能力存在“很大的不确定性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/risky-uk-mortgage-bonds-face-cash-flow-pressure-as-arrears-soar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 09:05:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
